reviewText: Boin Lecture, well the art work isnt the best I have seen, but the story is pretty dam good. I bought this because it's getting harder to find I was surprised Amazon had this, but then again they do find some of the best hentai or sellers that do. Look I will be straite with you I am a Disabled vet I have a spinal injury so I don't get out much. Anime is the one thing that takes me where I can't go and with some of the finest women artest can draw. I served my country with honor so I think I should have my little anime world anyway I like and this is just better than a lot of hentai I have seen. I know this may not be hard core but no one is tied up or raped. I don't tell people what is moraly right because I watch it too but I don't think Rape and violence is my cup of tea so that's why I picked this.
summary: Boin Lecture not the best but it's better than alot of them
